٤٩٧ - Islam And Orientalism: Maryam Jamila, Matbuaat -ul- Maktabat- il Ilmiyyah Lahore, Pakistan, ١٩٦٧.
٤٩٨ - Islam in Modern History: Cutwell Smith.
٤٩٩ - Life and Work of Sir Syed Ahmed Khan: H. A.R.Gipp,١٨٨٥.
٥٠٠ - Modern Islam: The Search for Cultural Identify: University of California Press, London, ١٩٦٢.
٥٠١ - Modern Islam in India: W.I.C. Smith, Sh. Muhammad Ashraf, Lahore, Pakistan, ١٩٦٣.
٥٠٢ - Modernization Menaces Muslims: Aslam Siddiqi, S.H. Muhammad Ashraf, Lahore, Pakistan, ١٩٧٤.
٥٠٣ - Modernization and Social Change Among Muslims in India: Patel Enterprises.
٥٠٤ - Muslim Shines in India: Christian W. Troll, Oxford University Press, ١٩٨٩.
٥٠٥ - Our Indian Muslims: W.W.Hunter, Iqbal Academy Lahor Pakistan.
٥٠٦ - Personal Reminisences of Sir Syed Ahmed: Asia Quart Rev.
٥٠٧ - Propossed Reforms: Charag Ali Bombay,١٨٨٣.
٥٠٨ - Religious Thought of Ahmed Khan: Eminent Mussalmans, ١٩٥٧.
٥٠٩ - Series of Essay on the life of Mohammed. Parvez and Co London.١٨٧٠.
٥١٠ - Syed Ahmed Khan a Religious Reformer: Shahdin, Hindustani Review, ١٩٠٤ ..
